descript.abstract: Generalized Zoning Coverage for the state of Oregon. The coverage is digitized from data collected from 1983 through 1986. Limited zoning changes have occured since this time. This dataset represents the best STATEWIDE zoning coverage available for the state of Oregon
descript.purpose: This data set was devleoped to show generalized zoning throughout the state of Oregon.
